#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:2
msgid ""
"New clients created by Terraform can be automatically registered to "
"{productname}.  Registration can be achieved in two ways:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:3
msgid "[literal]``cloud-init`` based registration"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:4
msgid "remote execution provisioner based registration"
msgstr ""

#. type: Title ==
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:5
#, no-wrap
msgid "[literal]``cloud-init`` Based Client Registration"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:6
msgid ""
"Registering by leveraging [literal]``cloud-init`` is the preferred way of "
"automatic registering of the newly created virtual machines.  This solution "
"avoids configuring an SSH connection to the host.  It can also be used "
"regardless of the tool used for client creation."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:7
msgid ""
"User can pass the set of user data when deploying the image with Terraform, "
"to automatically register the machine to {productname}.  [path]``user_data`` "
"is run only once at bootstrap, and only the first time the machine is "
"started."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:8
msgid ""
"Before using [literal]``cloud-init`` to register clients, the user must "
"configure:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:9
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:21
msgid ""
"Bootstrap script.  For more information, see xref:client-configuration:"
"registration-bootstrap.adoc[]."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:10
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:22
msgid ""
"Activation keys.  For more information, see xref:client-configuration:"
"activation-keys.adoc[]."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/automatic-client-registration.adoc:11
msgid ""
"The following command will download the bootstrap script and register the "
"new machine when it is created.  It should be added to the [literal]``cloud-"
"init`` configuration:"
