"Server, and have the [daemon]``libvirtd`` service running on the host."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/virt-xenkvm.adoc:99
msgid ""
"In the {productname} {webui}, navigate to menu:Systems[System List], and "
"click on the VM host for the guests you want to manage.  Navigate to the "
"[guimenu]``Virtualization`` tab to see all guests registered to this host, "
"and access the management functions."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/client-configuration/pages/virt-xenkvm.adoc:100
msgid ""
"For more information about managing VM guests using the {webui}, see xref:"
"reference:systems/system-details/sd-virtualization.adoc[]."
